				<td colspan="2"><span>Unless you have someone with good resist or you have low cha. Us bards have an excellent technique I call the mez and drain. This does take some time depending on who your fighitn with and what they have on them kei ft items and so on will slow it down.  essentialy what you do is mez your oppentent and keep them mezzed whlile you switch between our mez song and our mana drain song/songs depending on what lvl your at.  once you get them down to the point where they have very limited casting abilities if any the only thing you need to worry about are special skills  as any class besides bards are basicly melles when they are oom.
<br />

<br />
Once you get them oom mez them long enough to switch out to your chanting set or what ever you can use to fight them at a distance with  since they are now forced to melle you since they can not cast.
<br />

<br />
Repeat the mez mana drain combo if they continue to cast and then finish them off with a  distance dmging song of some kind.</span></td>
